Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=12}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Você nunca aprende, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.81,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let go! I'll pay later!-OG}Me solta! Eu pago depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:02.94,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Com meu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:03.65,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You fool! - OG}Você também não!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.61,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You made another boy cry?!-OG}Fez mais meninos chorarem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:07.57,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{He made me mad!-OG}Eles me irritaram!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:09.65,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem. Crianças são crianças.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.74,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{He said your tangerines\Nsuck, Bell-mère-san!-OG}Eles disseram que suas tangerinas são ruins!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:12.57,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say what?!-OG}Disseram o quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.57,0:02:13.53,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:16.45,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Não se renda a ninguém...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:21.41,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even girls need to be strong... - OG}Até garotas precisam ser fortes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:23.29,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't matter if\Npeople don't praise you!-OG}Não importa o que as pessoas pensam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.71,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't have hate for this\Nera you were born in... - OG}{Do not hate this era you were born in... - Gaijin}{Don't hate the times you live in.-Gaijin}Não culpe o mundo\Nem que nasceu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:34.47,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Never forget the strength to\Nbe able to smile at any time... - OG}{Don't forget how to smile,\Nno matter what happens.-Gaijin - Considerable adaption from the source, but I think this is far more natural.}E não importa o que aconteça,\Nnão esqueça de sorrir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:43.64,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2354)}– Bell-mère!\N– Bell-mère!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:49.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Under my rule,\Nanyone without money dies!-OG}Sob meu governo,\Nquem não puder pagar morre!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:52.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Understand, you inferior species?! - OG}{Understand, you worms?!-Gaijin}Entenderam, vermes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma carta náutica?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:01.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fui eu que desenhei! É importante pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You drew it?-OG}Você desenhou isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:06.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.97,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is quite impressive.-OG}Nada mal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She's an invaluable asset!\NBring her with us!-OG}Podemos usar essa pirralha! Peguem ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:17.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:19.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let go! Let go! No!-OG}Me solta! Me solta! Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:22.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Soltem a Nami! Soltem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:22.22,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:24.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês pegaram o dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You promised not to\Nlay a hand on her!-OG}Vocês juraram que não machucariam ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I ain't gonna hurt her.\NI'm just gonna borrow her.-OG}E não vou. Só estou\Npegando ela emprestada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san! Help!-OG}Sr. Gen, me ajuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Keep your hands off the children!-OG}Tirem as mãos delas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:34.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kuroobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen! Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:44.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:52.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll save you, Nami...-OG}Não se preocupe... Eu vou te salvar, Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:55.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you pass...-OG}Não vou deixar vocês passarem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não! Tudo bem!\NVocê não precisa me salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:00.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is getting tedious.-OG}Vamos acabar com isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou... salvar–
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please, no more dying! - OG}Eu não quero que mais ninguém morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:22.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All of the village's\Nships have been sunk... - OG}{They sank all the village's ships.-Gaijin}Eles afundaram todos\Nos nossos navios...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:26.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our idea of trying to let Nojiko\Nand Nami escape to sea... - OG}{Our idea of having Nojiko\Nand Nami escape to sea...-Gaijin}Nosso plano de mandar Nojiko\Ne Nami fugirem pelo mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{was too optimistic... - OG}{was pure fantasy.-Gaijin}foi otimista demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:31.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just as I feared,\Nthe Marines won't listen to us.-OG}Como eu temia,\Na Marinha não vai nos ajudar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This island will be under his control.-OG}Essa ilha é dele agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.38,0:04:35.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bell-mère knew!-OG}A Bell-mère sabia exatamente\No que ia acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:40.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She fully knew how they work\Nfrom her experience as a Marine!-OG}Ela sabia como piratas agem\Ndo tempo dela na Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:44.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She knew not a single person\Ncould ever escape...-OG}E ela sabia que ninguém\Nia escapar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:51.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles levaram a Nami com eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What...-OG}O que eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:55.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{am I supposed to do now...-OG}devo fazer agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:57.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:02.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Descobrimos onde\Nos Piratas do Arlong estão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que pretendem\Nse estabelecer nesta ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É hora de decidir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do we fight now and die defiantly?! - OG}{Do we fight now and\Ndie in defiance of their rule?!-Gaijin}{Do we die now, fighting in defiance?!-CPS, WF}Lutamos agora, desafiando até o fim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Or do we place our hope in waiting\Nfor help from the government,-OG}Ou esperamos, torcendo pra que\No governo venha nos resgatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{while living under the fear\Nof being killed at any time?! - OG}{while living under\Nthe constant fear of death?!-Gaijin}enquanto vivemos sob\No machado do executor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É um ou outro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:20.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só o Quartel-General da Marinha\Ntem chance contra eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:23.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But HQ has its hands\Nfull in the Grand Line.-Z - This would be an instance where the "HQ" acronym should be fine to leave as is since it was said in full in just the previous sentence.}Mas estão ocupados\Nna Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:28.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our hopes of them coming all the way\Nout here are as good as zero!-OG}{There's zero chance of them\Ncoming all the way out here!-WF}As chances de virem até aqui\Nsão praticamente nulas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:31.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I can't let Nami go!-OG}{But I can't just let them take Nami!-WF}E eu não posso abandonar a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:32.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Me, too!-OG}Eu também vou lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I doubt I can live my life\Nknowing I abandoned a child!-OG}Não posso seguir em frente\Nsabendo que abandonei uma criança!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:42.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're all family here!-OG}Todos aqui são família!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if it means I die killing them,\NI'm gonna save Nacchan! - OG}{Even if I die alongside them,\NI'm gonna save Nami!-Gaijin}Mesmo que eu morra lutando,\Nvou salvar a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bell-mère gave her life up\Nto protect them!-OG}A Bell-mère deu a vida\Npra proteger aquelas crianças!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's fight 'em again!-OG}Dessa vez, vamos dar o troco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They'll blame us all anyway\Nif just one of us fights! - OG}{They'll blame us all anyway\Nas long as any one of us fights!-Gaijin}Se qualquer um de nós revidar,\Ntodos seremos culpados de qualquer jeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nacchan!-OG}Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.43,0:06:05.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're all right?!-OG}Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:11.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está bem? Está machucada?\NEles fizeram alguma coisa com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou... me juntar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:19.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou me juntar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:23.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,aos Piratas do Arlong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to be a surveyor\Nand draw sea charts!-OG}pra desenhar cartas náuticas\Ncomo cartógrafa deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:34.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que está dizendo, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you in your right mind?-OG}Está pensando direito?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles fizeram algo\Nhorrível com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did they?-OG}Fizeram, não fizeram?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:41.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.51,0:06:42.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles te ameaçaram, né?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{didn't they?! Say it!-OG}Conta pra gente!
Comment: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,right?!{WF}
Comment: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Say something!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.84,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.89,0:06:48.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Th-That's an Arlong tattoo... - OG}{Th-That's Arlong's tattoo...-Gaijin}A-Aquela tatuagem... A bandeira do Arlong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:58.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Look at this...-OG}Olha só...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:04.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles me deram todo esse dinheiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And they say they'll\Nbuy me anything I want...-OG}e dizem que vão\Nme comprar tudo que eu quiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Unforgivable! Unforgivable! - OG}{Unforgivable! Shameful!-Gaijin}Imperdoável! Desprezível!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Joining pirates is\Nabsolutely unforgivable! - OG}{I absolutely can't forgive you\Nif you join those pirates!-Gaijin}{I can never forgive you\Njoining those pirates!-CPS, WF}Se juntar àqueles caras\Né absolutamente imperdoável!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And them, of all people!-OG}Com eles não! De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you even know what\Nkind of people they are?!-OG}Você não sabe que tipo\Nde gente eles são?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So what?!-OG}E daí?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I'm gonna get killed living\Na proper life like Bell-mère-san, - OG}{If living an honorable life\Ngets me killed like Bell-mère,-Gaijin}Se seguir as regras\Nme mata como a Bell-mère,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:29.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{then I don't wanna live properly! - OG}{then I don't wanna live honorably!-Gaijin}{then I'm not going to!-WF}então prefiro quebrá-las!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe this... - OG}Não acredito em você...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:39.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bell-mère-san was killed because of us! - OG}{Bell-mère died for us!-Gaijin}A Bell-mère sacrificou\Na vida pra nos salvar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você pode simplesmente–
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Já chega, Nojiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vá embora, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:46.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Never step foot into this village again!-OG}Nunca mais apareça\Nnesta vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.84,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{How could she be so foolish?-OG}Como ela pode ser tão cega?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:08.09,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did she not see\NBell-mère as her parent?!-OG}Ela nunca viu...\Na Bell-mère como mãe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:19.73,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, isso não é verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:23.57,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nami amava a Bell-mère...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:31.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bell-mère-san said...}A Bell-mère não disse...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:37.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that if we survive... - OG}que, se sobrevivêssemos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{fun things will happen, right? - OG}seríamos felizes um dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Lots of fun things... - OG}Ela disse que seríamos muito felizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.55,0:08:48.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Depois que o Arlong me levou,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,cinco navios da Marinha vieram\Npra capturá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{but they were all sunk easily... - OG}{but Arlong easily sank them-Gaijin}Ele afundou todos como se não fossem nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:57.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't think the government will\Nsend any more help to this island.-OG}Acho que eles não\Nvão mandar mais ajuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:01.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's what made me realize\NI have to do something.-OG}Então eu tenho que resolver\Nisso com as minhas próprias mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.35,0:09:04.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I made an agreement with Arlong...-OG}Eu fiz um acordo com o Arlong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to buy Cocoyashi Village from him.-OG}pra comprar a Vila Cocoyashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.65,0:09:08.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{To buy the village?-OG}A vila inteira?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por 100 milhões de berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If I buy the village, we can be free.-OG}Quando eu comprar, todos seremos livres.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém mais vai ter que morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{In exchange, I have to join his\Ngroup and draw sea charts. - OG}Em troca, tenho que me juntar à\Ntripulação dele e desenhar cartas náuticas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:23.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{B-But, 100 million berries?-OG}Mas cem milhões de berries?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm not sure you can earn that\Nmuch working your entire life–-OG}Como alguém conseguiria juntar–
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will earn it!-OG}Eu vou conseguir esse dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Custe o que custar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.96,0:09:33.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone's working their hardest\Nto pay the tribute money, so my only choice is to do it alone.-OG}{\q2}Como todos trabalham tanto\Npra juntar o tributo, estou sozinha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:37.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because if I ask for help from anyone,\Nmore people will get hurt. - OG}{If I ask anyone for help,\Nmore people will get hurt.-Gaijin}Se eu pedir ajuda a alguém,\Nmais pessoas vão se machucar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It'll hurt, you know... - OG}{You know, it won't be easy...-Gaijin}{It won't be easy, y'know...-WF}Não vai ser fácil, sabe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah... - OG}{I do.-WF}Eu sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:51.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ficar com as pessoas que\Nmataram a Bell-mère vai doer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:53.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou ficar bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:56.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll put on a big smile,\Neven when I see his face! - OG}Vou dar um grande sorriso,\Nmesmo quando olhar pra ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Decidi não chorar mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I've decided to fight on my own!-OG}De agora em diante,\Nvou lutar sozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you know how painful of a choice it was for Nami - OG}A Nami tinha apenas dez anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{to decide to fight and survive on her own, - OG}Imaginem como foi difícil a escolha
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:28.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{at the mere age of 10? - OG}de lutar e sobreviver sozinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:33.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For the only deal that could\Nsave the village...-OG}Pelo bem da vila dela,\Nela fez aquele acordo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.99,0:10:38.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll make whoever makes my\Nbeloved Nami-san suffer–-OG}Vou fazer aqueles desgraçados\Npagarem por machucar–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why, Big Sister?-OG}Por quê... Mana...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu avisei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:45.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I came here to stop you!-WF}Vim aqui pra dizer pra vocês pararem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you make a big fuss\Nabout her being your friend,-OG}Se ficarem falando\Nque são amigos dela,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{the pirates'll grow suspicious of Nami - OG}{the pirates'll grow suspicious of Nami.-Gaijin}O Arlong vai suspeitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and her eight years of fighting\Nwill be all for nothing! - OG}Os oito anos de luta dela\Nvão ser em vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't make her suffer\Nany more than she has. - OG}{Don't make her suffer\Nany more than she already has.-Gaijin}Ela já sofreu o bastante.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She has to fight alone,\Nso the most painful thing for her-OG}Quando você tem que lutar sozinha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:02.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{is having people who\Ncall her their friend!-OG}nada é mais doloroso\Ndo que pessoas te chamando de amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:19.62,FlashbacksSecondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Volta aqui! Pirralha maldita!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.12,FlashbacksSecondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Como ousa roubar nosso tesouro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:24.33,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Roubando de piratas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.12,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:29.59,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm using the huge number of pirates\Nin this era to my advantage!-OG}Hoje em dia, o mar está lotado\Ndeles! Então estou lucrando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.88,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's like, "You get what you deserve!"-OG}{They deserve nothing less!-WF}É o que eles merecem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.22,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're covered in cuts, though!-OG}Mas você está toda machucada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.22,0:11:38.18,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I sorta screwed up.\NBut look at this! One million berries!-OG}É, eu meio que vacilei.\NMas olha só! Um milhão de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.85,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Forget that! You need\Nmedical treatment, quick! - OG}{Forget about that!\NWe need to treat those cuts, quick!-Gaijin}E daí?! Precisamos\Ncuidar desses cortes rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.77,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou bem! Não é nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:46.10,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Ninguém nunca vai achar aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.81,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll gather money little by little, - OG}Vou guardar meu dinheiro\Naqui, pouco a pouco,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:51.32,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{and it'll be 100 million\Nwhen I'm grown up! - OG}{and it'll be 100 million\Nby the time it's full!-Gaijin}e quando estiver cheio,\Nvou ter 100 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.82,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I have a long ways to go... - OG}Tenho um longo caminho pela frente...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:00.03,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{A hundred million berries...-OG}Cem milhões de berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:06.62,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's taken a long time... but just seven million left... - OG}{but I just need seven million more.-Gaijin}{It's taken a long time... but I only\Nneed another seven million berries.-WF}Levou muito tempo...\Nmas faltam só sete milhões.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:09.83,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can earn that much now in one try! - OG}{I can earn that much now in one run!-Gaijin}Hoje em dia, consigo\Nessa grana numa viagem só!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:11.75,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Só...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.80,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{one more journey,\Nand it'll all be over...-OG}mais uma viagem\Ne finalmente vai acabar...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:20.89,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone in Cocoyashi Village\Nand I will be free of Arlong.-OG}Todos na Vila Cocoyashi—\Ne eu—seremos livres do Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.51,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,E então...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:25.02,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,E então, eu acho...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.73,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,vou finalmente poder sorrir\Ndo fundo do meu coração...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.27,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Bell-mère.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What do the Marines want with Nami?-OG}Que assunto a Marinha\Ntem com a Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:56.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You simply need to\Nlead the way quietly. - OG}{You simply need to\Nkeep quiet and lead the way.-Gaijin}Não precisa fazer perguntas.\NSó mostre o caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.30,0:13:03.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why does that old guy have\Na pinwheel on his head?-OG}Por que aquele cara tem\Num catavento na cabeça?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.85,0:13:05.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So cool!-OG}Demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Guess I'll get started on\Nmy final plunder run!-Gaijin}{Guess I'll get started on\Nmy final act of plundering!-OG}Acho que vou começar\Nmeu último golpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E a Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you the girl thief known as Nami? - OG}{Are you the thief known as Nami?-Gaijin}Você é a ladra chamada Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:37.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our information has it you've hidden\Ntreasure you stole from pirates.-OG}Recebemos uma denúncia de que você\Nestá escondendo tesouros roubados de piratas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:43.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The government hereby takes possession\Nof everything you stole from the pirates.-OG}{As such, the government hereby\Ntakes possession of said treasure.-WF}E todos os bens saqueados\Nsão propriedade do governo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here's a warning for you.-OG}Vou te dar um aviso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm a leader of the Arlong Pirates. - OG}Sou uma oficial dos Piratas do Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:53.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mess with me, and Arlong\Nwon't sit by quietly! - OG}Mexa comigo e o Arlong\Nnão vai ficar parado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:55.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Garota boba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:59.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você acha que está lidando\Ncomigo de igual pra igual?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Encontrem os bens roubados!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stop!-OG}Não se atrevam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:19.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is this what the Marines\Nshould be doing right now?!-OG}É isso que a Marinha\Ndeveria estar fazendo agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:23.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Arlong Pirates have killed people,\Nand even destroyed towns!-OG}Os Piratas do Arlong assassinaram\Ninocentes e destruíram cidades inteiras!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você sabe disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:29.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's ruling over this island\Nand trampling all over people's lives!-OG}Ele governa esta ilha com mão de ferro,\Npisoteando vidas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is ignoring that major problem-OG}É assim que o governo funciona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.06,0:14:34.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and raking in stolen goods from a thief\Nwhat the government stands for?! - OG}{and snatching stolen goods from a thief\Nwhat the government stands for?!-Gaijin}Prendendo ladrõezinhos enquanto\Nfaz vista grossa pra tudo isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't talk all big. - OG}Cuidado com a forma que fala comigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Continue your search!-OG}Continuem procurando!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:44.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{People all over the island have been\Nwaiting for your help for years now!-OG}{\q2}Há anos as pessoas desta ilha\Nestão esperando vocês virem ajudá-las!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.91,0:14:48.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How dare you just pass\Nthem by and come here!-OG}Como pode simplesmente\Nignorar todos por causa disso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:51.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Capitão! Esse pomar de\Ntangerinas parece suspeito!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:52.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cavem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:59.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tirem suas mãos sujas do\Npomar de tangerinas da Bell-mère!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I won't let you have my money!-OG}Não vou deixar vocês pegarem esse dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:06.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That money's for...\NThat money's for...-OG}Esse dinheiro é... Esse dinheiro é...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This girl's money is meant to save Cocoyashi Village! - OG}{Her money is meant\Nto save Cocoyashi Village!-Gaijin}{That money is meant\Nto save Cocoyashi Village!-WF}Esse dinheiro é a chave\Npra liberdade da Vila Cocoyashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What gives you the right\Nto take it away, navy man?! - OG}Que direito você tem\Nde tirá-lo, Fuzileiro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:23.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A lowly village representative,\Ntalking down to a Marine captain? - OG}{A lowly village representative,\Nchallenging a naval captain?-Gaijin}Um xerife de vila do interior\Nrespondendo a um capitão da Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:28.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe disso?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.12,0:15:34.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu sempre soube, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:39.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I couldn't believe\Nwhat you'd done then, - OG}{I couldn't believe\Nwhat you did back then,-Gaijin}Naquela época, não consegui\Nacreditar no que você fez,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:41.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so I confronted Nojiko later.-OG}então confrontei a Nojiko depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Todo mundo na vila\Nsabe desde então
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:48.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that you stayed with the Arlong Pirates\Nso you could save the village.-OG}que você ficou com os Piratas\Ndo Arlong pra salvar a vila.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But we pretended we didn't know. - OG}{We only pretended we didn't know.-Gaijin}{We only pretended not to know.-WF}Nós só fingimos não saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because our hopes would keep you - OG}Achávamos que nossas esperanças\Nte impediriam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:58.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,de fugir do Arlong,\Nse algum dia decidisse fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:05.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What on earth are you talking about? - OG}Do que diabos está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:10.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está dizendo que todos\Nos moradores são ladrões,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:11.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e que devemos prendê-los?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:16.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's saying that each and every\None of us is fighting to live!-OG}Ele está dizendo que cada um\Nde nós está lutando pra sobreviver!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:20.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But only because we can't rely\Non any of you government people!-OG}Mas só porque não podemos\Ncontar com o governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:24.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you're not gonna save our village,\Nthen get the hell out of here!-OG}Se não veio nos ajudar,\Nentão cai fora daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:28.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dilly-dally, and Arlong'll\Ngo after your ship, too!-OG}Continue com essa palhaçada e\No Arlong afunda seu navio também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mr. Arlong will?-OG}Arlong, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não teria tanta certeza...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ainda não acharam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:39.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estamos procurando 100 milhões de\Nberries! Não um grão de arroz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:42.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe\Nquanto tem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:47.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, os 100 milhões?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:51.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I just got the feeling\Nthere's that much.-OG}Bom, digamos que foi um palpite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que o Arlong mandou vocês aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who knows?-OG}Quem sabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:21.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're simply dealing with theft\Nas any government workers would. - OG}Estamos apenas lidando com roubo\Ncomo qualquer funcionário público faria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What rotten scum!-OG}Malditos capangas do governo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I can't believe the Marines would\Nstoop to being pirate cronies!-OG}Como a Marinha pode\Nse rebaixar a ser lacaios de piratas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.24,0:17:30.74,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Achei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm impressed you could gather this much, girl! - OG}{I'm impressed a girl like you\Ncould gather this much!-Gaijin}Pensar que uma garota como você\Nconseguiu juntar tudo isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Está todo surrado e\Nmanchado de sangue...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não importa! Dinheiro é dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.35,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Thirty percent of this is all mine!-OG}E trinta por cento é todo meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não toque nisso...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.77,0:18:02.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não toque nisso... Não toque nisso...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não toque nisso...!\NNão toque nisso...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não toque nisso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:31.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Doutor! Doutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Sr. Gen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:46.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Nojiko levou um tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:48.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Marinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:49.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:55.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Heya, Nami!-OG}Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:19:00.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E aí? Precisa de ajuda com alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:04.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Are you still here?!-OG}Você ainda está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This has nothing to do with you!\NLeave the damn island already!-OG}Isso não tem nada a ver com você!\NSai logo dessa ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.68,0:19:17.22,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.14,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do you want me to return\Nthe village that badly?-OG}Você quer mesmo que eu\Nliberte sua vila assim tanto?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:22.18,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.19,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gather up 100 million berries\Nand bring it here.-OG}Junte 100 milhões de berries\Ne traga pra mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:28.98,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do so, and I'll let the village go\Nand give you freedom.-OG}Se fizer isso, eu libero você\Ne a vila.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.73,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.99,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'd die before I break an\Nagreement concerning money.-OG}{I'd rather die than break\Na deal involving money.-That's his ninja way, WF}Quando se trata de dinheiro,\Nprefiro morrer a quebrar uma promessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.11,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{It doesn't matter\Nhow many years it takes.-OG}Não me importo quanto tempo leve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.78,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll honor our agreement.-OG}{I'll honor our deal.-WF}Sou um homem-peixe de palavra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's her problem?-OG}Cara, qual é o problema dela?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:51.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:58.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's wrong,\Nskilled surveyor of ours?-OG}Por que a cara fechada,\Nminha capaz cartógrafa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why the angry look? - OG}{What's with the angry look?-Gaijin}Por que a carranca?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:04.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The Navy men you have under\Nyour control stole all my money! - OG}{The Marines you have under\Nyour control stole all my money!-Z - "Navy men" again.}Aqueles Fuzileiros que você\Npaga roubaram todo o meu dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:09.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What happened to dying before\Nbreaking promises about money?!-OG}{What happened to dying before\Nbreaking deals involving money?!-WF}Eu pensei que quando se tratasse de dinheiro,\Nvocê preferia morrer a quebrar uma promessa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{When did I break our promise?-OG}E quando exatamente\Neu quebrei nossa promessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't play dumb! You teamed up\Nwith the Marines to–-OG}Não venha com essa!\NOs Fuzileiros que você–
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{When did I break our promise?-OG}Como eu disse, quando\Neu quebrei nossa promessa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:22.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fala!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.17,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:34.25,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito! Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I see!-OG}Ah, agora entendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então seu dinheiro foi roubado?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How unfortunate.-OG}Que pena.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.72,0:20:44.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But an agreement is an agreement.-OG}Mas, ei. Um acordo é um acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:47.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you can't  gather up\N100 million berries for me to see, - OG}{If you can't bring\N100 million berries to me,-Gaijin}Se você não pode me trazer 100 milhões de berries,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm afraid I can't give\Nyou the village back.-OG}infelizmente não posso devolver sua vila.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Scum! - OG}{You scum!-Gaijin}Seu canalha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's only 100 million berries!-OG}Ei, são só 100 milhões de berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É só começar a juntar de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Or are you gonna run out on me?-OG}Ou talvez esteja pensando\Nem fugir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:13.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But if you do run away,\NI'll kill everyone in Cocoyashi Village.-OG}Só lembre que, se fizer isso,\Nvou matar todos na Vila Cocoyashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.92,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:21.68,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{We pretended we didn't know. - OG}{We only pretended we didn't know.-Gaijin}Nós só fingimos não saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:24.93,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Because our hopes would keep you - OG}Achávamos que nossas esperanças\Nte impediriam
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:28.73,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,935)}de fugir do Arlong,\Nse algum dia decidisse fazer isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.65,0:21:36.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Finally running away, huh?-OG}Fugindo afinal, é?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Shouldn't we chase after her?-OG}Não devíamos perseguir ela?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:43.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Perseguir? Pra quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:46.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela não vai fugir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:51.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ela nunca abandonaria\Na vida dos moradores.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você realmente sabe\Njogar sujo...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:59.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No way would I let such an exceptional\Nsurveyor as Nami go so easily.-OG}Como se eu fosse deixar uma\Ncartógrafa do calibre da Nami ir embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I'm not a heartless devil.-OG}Mas não sou totalmente insensível.
Comment: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:07.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Once she's done surveying\Nall of the world's seas,-OG}She just needs to chart\Nevery sea in the world.{WF}
Comment: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll give her her freedom!-OG}Then{\i0} I'll let her go!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.18,0:22:09.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou deixá-la ir, claro... depois que ela mapear todos os mares do mundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:15.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's like decades from now! - OG}Isso vai levar décadas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not even a hundred\Nyears'd be enough!-OG}Não daria pra fazer isso\Nnem em cem anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:28.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No more of this!\NTake up your weapons!-OG}Chega! Peguem suas armas!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's fight!-OG}Vamos lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:38.75,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Mr. Gen-san! Everyone!\NPlease! Don't be hasty!-OG}Sr. Gen! Pessoal!\NPor favor, não façam besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.42,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês não podem morrer! Vai acabar tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.01,0:22:45.14,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{You have to survive,\Nor everything will end!-OG}Vocês precisam sobreviver,\Nou tudo terá sido em vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:47.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oito anos atrás...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:50.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we swore we'd keep on living!-WF}juramos não jogar nossas vidas fora!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:53.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter how painful and insulting\Nit was to be ruled by them,-OG}Não importa o quão\Nhumilhante fosse o governo deles,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:58.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we swore to fight the patient fight\Nas long as Nami was cheerful!-OG}juramos que aguentaríamos pacientemente\Nenquanto a Nami continuasse sorrindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:01.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas essa é a resposta deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.74,0:23:06.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now that our village's chance for\Nfreedom is gone, we have no hope!-OG}{\q2}Agora que a única chance de liberdade\Nda nossa vila acabou, não há mais esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:07.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{More than that,-OG}Acima de tudo,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.78,0:23:12.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we must make those fishmen pay\Nfor toying with that girl's kindness!-OG}temos que fazer aqueles homens-peixe pagarem\Npor brincar com o coração daquela garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Any objections?!-OG}Concordam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:15.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course not! Let's go!-OG}Claro! Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:19.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We were always fully ready\Nto fight at any time!-OG}Nos últimos oito anos,\Nsempre estivemos prontos pra lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:22.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I refuse to let them rule\Nover me any more!-OG}Nem morto passo mais\Num dia sob o governo deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:26.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esperem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:29.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:33.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só mais um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:35.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só esperem mais um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:37.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll keep working hard!-Gaijin}Vou trabalhar duro de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:39.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou juntar o dinheiro de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:41.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai ser fácil dessa vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:46.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm used to it! I'll be fine!\NThere's no need to worry at all!-OG}Estou acostumada! Vai ficar tudo bem!\NNão tem nada com que se preocupar!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso não é nada\Ncomparado àquela época!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:53.79,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please, no more dying! - OG}Eu não quero que mais ninguém morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.20,0:23:55.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.41,0:23:58.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm fine! I'm just fine!-OG}Estou bem, de verdade! Vai ficar tudo bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:05.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You can stop now.-OG}Já chega.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.59,0:24:07.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even you know there's no point now.-OG}Até você sabe que acabou.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:13.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You fought very well, carrying\Nour lives on your back all this time...-OG}{\q2}{You've done so well, bearing the burden\Nof this entire village for years...-WF}Você foi tão corajosa, carregando o peso\Nda vila inteira por todos esses anos...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:16.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Joining them must've been\Neven more painful for you-OG}Se juntar a eles deve ter doído mais
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:18.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{than being cut through the heart.-OG}do que ser apunhalada no coração.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:22.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You fought very well.-OG}Você se saiu muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:25.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:33.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saia da vila agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.08,0:24:35.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sr. Gen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.87,0:24:38.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:39.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.46,0:24:41.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nacchan...-OG}Nami, querida...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:42.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.67,0:24:46.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're crafty, and you\Nhave your dream.-OG}Você tem um sonho e sabe\Ncuidar de si mesma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.92,0:24:48.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nojiko! Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.18,0:24:51.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou deixar vocês irem!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.68,0:24:54.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parem com isso, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:57.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't want to see anyone\Nelse get hurt by them!-OG}Não aguento ver mais ninguém se machucar!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.69,0:25:00.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'll die, you know!-OG}Eles vão matar vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.81,0:25:03.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A gente sabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.99,0:25:12.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não adianta! Já nos decidimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:17.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sai do caminho, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.62,0:25:21.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.17,0:25:24.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if we can't win, let's\Nshow 'em what we're made of!-OG}Mesmo que não possamos vencer,\Nvamos dar o troco!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.58,0:26:03.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.71,0:26:07.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.59,0:26:10.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.34,0:26:14.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Arlong! Arlong! Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.89,0:26:15.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ar–
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.10,0:26:22.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.19,0:26:27.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.65,0:26:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You don't even know anything.-OG}Você não sabe de nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.78,0:26:33.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You don't even know what's happened\Non this island the past eight years! - OG}{You have no clue what's happened\Nhere for the past eight years!-Gaijin}{\q2}Você não faz ideia do que está\Nacontecendo aqui nos últimos oito anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.57,0:26:35.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. I don't know.-OG}Não, eu não sei.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.12,0:26:37.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso não tem nada a ver com você!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.54,0:26:41.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I told you, leave\Nthe damn island already! - OG}{I told you to leave\Nthe damn island already!-Gaijin}Eu já disse pra você sair\Ndessa ilha maldita!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.16,0:26:43.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. You told me. - OG}{Yeah. You did.-Gaijin}É, disse.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.16,0:26:44.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Leave!-OG}Então, vai embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.42,0:26:45.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não preciso de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.79,0:26:48.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Leave! Leave! Leave!-OG}Some! Vai! Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.13,0:26:49.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Leave!-OG}Vai embora!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.38,0:26:52.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Leave! Leave! Leave!-OG}Desaparece! Sai daqui! Vai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:54.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai embora...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.81,0:27:08.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.48,0:27:11.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me ajuda...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:26.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Claro que vou!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.54,0:27:31.71,Flashbacks-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't touch my treasure!-OG}Tirem as mãos do meu tesouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:35.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.68,0:27:42.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:45.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(232.5,1053)}{Yeah!-OG}Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:45.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1053)}{Yeah!-OG}Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:45.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1206,1053)}{Yeah!-OG}Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.52,0:27:50.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:52.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vocês estão bem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.36,0:27:54.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Arlong fez isso com vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.86,0:27:57.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Saiam do caminho.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.95,0:28:00.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Temos assuntos com os homens-peixe.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.33,0:28:03.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now that we know the truth\Nabout Big Sis Nami,-OG}Quando descobrimos\Na verdade sobre a Mana Nami,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.83,0:28:07.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{we felt the only thing\Nwe can do was defeat Arlong.-OG}sentimos que tudo que podíamos fazer\Nera tentar derrotar o Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:10.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então desafiamos ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.34,0:28:12.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,...mas perdemos por pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:19.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but we're not letting\Nyou through this door,\Nseeing as you have no hope for victory! - OG}{Sorry, but we're not letting you through here,\Nseeing as you have no hope for victory!-Gaijin}Desculpa, mas não podemos deixar vocês passarem!\NVocês não têm chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.05,0:28:20.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.35,0:28:24.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We're waiting here for\Ncertain men to arrive here, you see! - OG}{We're waiting here for\Na group of men, you see!-Gaijin}Estamos esperando uma\Ncerta tripulação aparecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.06,0:28:26.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Certain men? - OG}{A group of men?-Gaijin}Uma certa tripulação?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.98,0:28:28.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aposto minha vida nisso.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.10,0:28:31.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles vão vir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.70,0:28:47.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{– Here they come!\N– Here they come!-OG}– São eles!\N– São eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.92,0:28:51.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Move aside.-OG}{Let me through!-WF}Saiam do caminho!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.09,0:29:02.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, do you think those two idiots\Nwere part of Zoro's group?-OG}Ei, acha que aqueles dois palhaços\Nfaziam parte da tripulação do Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.30,0:29:06.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do Zoro? Pareciam\Nfracos demais pra isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.06,0:29:07.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nem vale a pena matar.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.73,0:29:09.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's for sure!-OG}Tem razão!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:24.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What the...?! - OG}Que diabos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.12,0:29:29.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Qual de vocês é o Arlong?!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=13}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=34}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
